<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Uffenheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Gewichtmeister zu Nürnberg das übersandte Gewicht überprüft und besiegelt haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_86" id="42r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_86_r1l20">Der Stat ʒu Vffenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_86_r1l21"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von ſölıchs gevvıchts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l23"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_86_r1l22">ʒu </ab></add> vns bey <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> habt geſant etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l24"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnde von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l25">Darcʒu <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>geſwor<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gewıchtmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> / <expan>daſſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> gewıcht 
<del rend="strikethrough"> gen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l26">nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gewıcht <expan>rechfertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd wıe ſıe das <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l27"><expan>yegleıche<ex>n</ex></expan> ſtuk ein ʒettel <expan>beſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>petſchet</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l28">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l29"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_86" id="42r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu Uffenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt von sölichs gewichts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <add>zu</add> uns bey <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> habt gesant etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        rate darczu <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan>, die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geswor<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gewichtmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dass<ex>elb</ex></expan> gewicht nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        gewicht <expan>rechfertig<ex>en</ex></expan>, und wie sie das
                                <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu <expan>yegleiche<ex>n</ex></expan> stuk ein
                        zettel <expan>beschreibe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>petschet</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonii.</ab>
</div>
